91b2d776-3cba-407f-9148-24fdafa1cfb9.0cfdc4b2-ae7f-4828-9bd5-a57b8695a9cc.prompt=User Identifier 91b2d776-3cba-407f-9148-24fdafa1cfb9.0e95fd22-9c9f-4e88-8ec7-89af48cd5e35.prompt=Enter a value for lockId 91b2d776-3cba-407f-9148-24fdafa1cfb9.12a493ad-234f-497b-aefe-5d803582f995.description=
Check to see if the value stored in a specified flow variable, denoted by key, is null.

Inputs\:
keyName - The key to check, i.e. the name of the flow variable.

Returns\: 
The value in the specified key, i.e. flow variable.

Responses\:
isNull - If the key is a null pointer, i.e. the flow variable doesn't have an assigned value.
notNull - If some value is stored in the key, i.e the flow variable has a value assigned.
91b2d776-3cba-407f-9148-24fdafa1cfb9.1b33221e-642b-4123-91fd-f606aaa1273c.description=This workflow adds/ updates the component properties to Instance using Artifact APIs. onlyUpdate\: yes/no yes - To update values of existing properties no - To add and/or update properties keyValuePairs\: If you want to Add/update new properties\: property1 PUBLIC INTEGER 5 property2 PUBLIC STRING abc xyz If you want to only update the values of existing properties\: property1 5 property2 abc xyz 91b2d776-3cba-407f-9148-24fdafa1cfb9.22bef620-a939-4025-8e2f-1f686d580fdb.prompt=User Identifier 91b2d776-3cba-407f-9148-24fdafa1cfb9.25f835ac-e8c9-4a33-9267-61ca16223664.description=This workflow adds/ updates the component properties to Instance using Artifact APIs. onlyUpdate\: yes/no yes - To update values of existing properties no - To add and/or update properties keyValuePairs\: If you want to Add/update new properties\: property1 PUBLIC INTEGER 5 property2 PUBLIC STRING abc xyz If you want to only update the values of existing properties\: property1 5 property2 abc xyz 91b2d776-3cba-407f-9148-24fdafa1cfb9.27895f99-7beb-4160-b23c-d428eaba1f3d.description=This workflow adds/ updates the component properties to Instance using Artifact APIs. onlyUpdate\: yes/no yes - To update values of existing properties no - To add and/or update properties keyValuePairs\: If you want to Add/update new properties\: property1 PUBLIC INTEGER 5 property2 PUBLIC STRING abc xyz If you want to only update the values of existing properties\: property1 5 property2 abc xyz 91b2d776-3cba-407f-9148-24fdafa1cfb9.9acf2297-fa12-4549-a2ac-7a9e25af645c.prompt=Enter a value for lockId 91b2d776-3cba-407f-9148-24fdafa1cfb9.9e002465-51aa-46e6-b09f-ad8fcc6287c4.prompt=User Identifier 91b2d776-3cba-407f-9148-24fdafa1cfb9.ad291870-77a6-4725-8ecf-a8aa86d32fa9.description=Releases a lock with an id given by the value of the lockId input. 
Inputs\:
   lockId - the id of the lock, maximum 255 characters.

Responses\:
   success - the only response returned.

Results\:
   there are no results.

Notes\:
1) The operation only releases locks acquired by the current run. 
   It cannot release another run's locks.

2) The operation succeeds whether or not there is a lock held 
   by the current run with the supplied id.
91b2d776-3cba-407f-9148-24fdafa1cfb9.b7524ec1-be3b-4415-b8b7-d1d6428e8ec7.description=Attempts to acquire the specified lock, and sleeps until the lock is available. 
Inputs\:
   lockId - the id of the lock, maximum 255 characters.
   timeout - The maximum number of seconds this flow will run for.
  seconds - The number of seconds to sleep for between each attempt at acquiring the lock.

Responses\:
   success - if the lock has been successfully acquired.
   failure - if the lock could not be acquired.

Result\:
   Code - 0 if the operation succeeds, 1 otherwise.

Notes\:
1) The locks acquired by this operation are not reentrant. This means that 
   once a lock is acquired by a run, all subsequent attempts at acquiring 
   the same lock by the same run (or any other run) will fail.

2) Once a run terminates, all the locks that were acquired during its execution
   are automatically released.
